{
  "stem": "13524.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or they'd just shoot you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, look.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see a person approaching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there go the SS men, normal, not shouting, not being conspicuous in any way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were walking into the ghetto for no reason, or to go to the office.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And out of, out of a blue, they pulled out a gun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They shot somebody for no reason whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the best way was just to go on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't stop to give help to that person who was lying dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just went on as if nothing happened, you didn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you managed to get to the first available gate, to avoid the SS turning around and shooting you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, I have seen that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what was going through your mind, while that was-- while you were going through the first gate?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not even terrified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Numbness.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Total numbness.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Total numbness.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I came home and I told my mother and my father what has happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They already knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Ghetto was fairly small.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that just-- they impressed more upon me I shouldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I should stay inside the room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All we had in ghetto was a tiny little room-- window, bed, curtain-- where my parents slept.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were at the other end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Stove for cooking, if there was anything to cook.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was a young girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was to be scooped up in that way for a long period, it was not very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So one would venture, in spite of the fact that it was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a dentist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I used to look for excuse to go to that dentist, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was a very good dentist and very pleasant-looking.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
